OL,6,FTwice a week, volunteers at the Hyson
OL,7,FGreen Youth Centre prepare food for up
OL,8,Fto 70 people struggling to afford a
OL,9,Fregular hot meal, but they're worried
OL,10,Fthey'll struggle to cope with extra
OL,11,Fdemand.JRyan Vaughan, Head Chef, said:
OL,12,F"Here they can come and get their hot
OL,13,Fmeal. It's raining, it's cold outside,
OL,14,Fthey get out of the rain, they come
OL,15,Fin, they're nice and warm. They get a
OL,16,Fwholesome, nutritious meal. No cost is
OL,17,Fspared."
