OL,6,FWhile Emmanuel Israel, a volunteer,
OL,7,Fadded: "We're all volunteers here
OL,8,Fbecause we all understand how it feels
OL,9,Fto be struggling, and to do your best.
OL,10,FSo it's very good to see that, but
OL,11,Fthen again there's a lot of people
OL,12,Fstruggling."
OL,14,FThe project was set-up with an initial
OL,15,Fone-off grant from the city council.
