OL,6,FBut with the local authority now
OL,7,Flooking at axing jobs and services to
OL,8,Fplug a #53 million gap in its budget,
OL,9,Fthe group fear any further funding
OL,10,Fwill dry up.JLorraine, one of the many
OL,11,Fvolunteers at the centre, said: "It
OL,12,Fwill affect what we do because we
OL,13,Fwon't be able to provide for the
OL,14,Fpeople. So that would be a loss to the
OL,15,Fcommunity. That would be a loss to the
OL,16,Fpeople that are benefitting from it.
OL,17,FSo we really don't need those cuts to
OL,18,Fhappen."
