OL,6,FToday, the campaign group Resolve
OL,7,FNottingham, set up to fight the cuts
OL,8,Fin the city, handed in a petition to
OL,9,FDowning Street, demanding more
OL,10,Fgovernment money for the city.
OL,12,FMutsa Makaka, Founder of the Changing
OL,13,FYour Mindset Charity, said: "The city
OL,14,Fis made by the people. And if the
OL,15,Fpeople are not getting the service, if
OL,16,Fthere isn't that community spirit, if
OL,17,Fthere isn't that community cohesion,
OL,18,Fif there isn't that support to
OL,19,Fempower, inspire, and heal, then what
OL,20,Fare we doing?"
