OL,6,FWhile Marcellus Baz, the founder of
OL,7,FSwitch Up, said: "We've already seen
OL,8,Fthe pandemic. Then we've seen the cost
OL,9,Fof living crisis. My concerns are that
OL,10,Fwith further cuts to our communities,
OL,11,Fit's going to have a catastrophic
OL,12,Feffect on people's livelihoods, on
OL,13,Fpeople's mental health. We're going to
OL,14,Fsee crime rates going up."JYesterday
OL,15,Fthe government approved access to
OL,16,Femergency loans for councils in acute
OL,17,Ffinancial distress. Nottingham has
OL,18,Fsecured just over #66 million, but in
OL,19,Freturn will need to look at other ways
OL,20,Fof raising revenue, including selling
OL,21,Foff assets.
